<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Letters — RWC Knowledge Hub</title>
<style>
:root {
  --teal:#04979c; --aqua:#00c4cc; --aqua-light:#79ced8;
  --aqua-pale:#e8f9fa; --aqua-mid:#d0f0f2;
  --ink:#0d1f22; --ink-soft:#2a4a4e; --ink-muted:#6b9196;
  --cream:#f7fafa; --white:#ffffff;
  --gold:#e8a838; --gold-light:#fef8ec;
  --red:#e05252; --red-light:#fff0f0;
  --green:#2d9e6b; --green-light:#edf9f4;
  --purple:#7c3aed; --purple-light:#f5f3ff;
  --blue:#2563eb; --blue-light:#eff6ff;
  --border:#d4ecee; --border-soft:#e8f4f5;
  --shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(4,151,156,.10);
  --shadow-lg:0 8px 40px rgba(4,151,156,.16);
  --shadow-card:0 1px 8px rgba(13,31,34,.07);
}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);min-height:100vh;}

/* HEADER — matches hub exactly */
.header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ink) 0%,#163a3f 60%,#0d5257 100%);padding:0 40px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:64px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:300;border-bottom:2px solid var(--teal);box-shadow:0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.3);}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;text-decoration:none;}
.logo-mark{width:36px;height:36px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal),var(--aqua));border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-1px;box-shadow:0 0 16px rgba(0,196,204,.4);}
.logo-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;letter-spacing:.2px;}
.logo-sub{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:1px;}

/* TAB BAR — matches hub exactly */
.tab-bar{background:var(--white);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;padding:0 40px;position:sticky;top:64px;z-index:200;box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow-x:auto;}
.tab{padding:14px 18px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink-muted);border-bottom:2px solid transparent;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;user-select:none;white-space:nowrap;text-decoration:none;}
.tab:hover{color:var(--teal);}
.tab.active{color:var(--teal);border-bottom-color:var(--teal);font-weight:600;}
.tab-ai{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;background:var(--teal);color:#fff;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:8px;}

/* MAIN */
.main{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px 40px 60px;}

/* HERO */
.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ink) 0%,#163a3f 60%,#0d5257 100%);border-radius:14px;padding:32px 36px;margin-bottom:24px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 70% at 85% 50%,rgba(0,196,204,.1) 0%,transparent 70%);}
.hero::after{content:'';position:absolute;right:-30px;top:-30px;width:140px;height:140px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--aqua);opacity:.08;}
.hero *{position:relative;z-index:1;}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--aqua);margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.hero-eyebrow::before{content:'';width:20px;height:1.5px;background:var(--aqua);}
.hero h1{font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:400;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:-.3px;}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--aqua-light);}
.hero p{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);line-height:1.7;max-width:520px;}

/* HIPAA BANNER */
.hipaa{background:var(--blue-light);border:1px solid #B5D4F4;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 14px;font-size:12px;color:#0C447C;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:20px;}

/* SUB NAV */
.subnav{display:flex;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:22px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.stab{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink-muted);padding:11px 15px;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1px;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;background:transparent;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-right:none;font-family:inherit;}
.stab:hover{color:var(--teal);}
.stab.on{color:var(--teal);border-bottom-color:var(--teal);font-weight:600;}

/* SUB PANELS */
.sub{display:none;}.sub.on{display:block;}

/* TIERS */
.tier{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;}
.t-self{background:var(--green-light);color:#085041;}
.t-mgmt{background:var(--gold-light);color:#633806;}
.t-owner{background:var(--red-light);color:#791F1F;}

/* DECISION NODES */
.dn{border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:10px;border:1px solid;}
.dn-start{background:var(--green-light);border-color:#9FE1CB;}
.dn-q{background:#f7f6f2;border-color:#d3d1c7;}
.dn-stop{background:var(--red-light);border-color:#F7C1C1;}
.dn-go{background:var(--green-light);border-color:#9FE1CB;}
.dn-warn{background:var(--gold-light);border-color:#FAC775;}
.dn-blue{background:var(--blue-light);border-color:#B5D4F4;}
.dn-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:7px;}
.dn-stop .dn-title{color:#791F1F;}.dn-go .dn-title{color:#085041;}.dn-warn .dn-title{color:#633806;}.dn-start .dn-title{color:#085041;}.dn-blue .dn-title{color:#0C447C;}.dn-q .dn-title{color:var(--ink);}
.dn p{font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:9px;}
.dn-stop p{color:#a32d2d;}.dn-go p{color:#085041;}.dn-warn p{color:#854f0b;}.dn-blue p{color:#0C447C;}.dn-q p{color:var(--ink-muted);}

.cbtn{display:block;width:100%;text-align:left;padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:7px;background:#fff;color:var(--ink);font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:5px;transition:all .15s;line-height:1.5;}
.cbtn:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
.cbtn:hover{background:#f0efe9;border-color:#999;}
.cbtn-stop:hover{background:var(--red-light);border-color:#F7C1C1;color:#791F1F;}
.cbtn-go:hover{background:var(--green-light);border-color:#9FE1CB;color:#085041;}
.cbtn-blue:hover{background:var(--blue-light);border-color:#B5D4F4;color:#0C447C;}
.reset-link{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted);cursor:pointer;text-decoration:underline;margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;}
.reset-link:hover{color:var(--teal);}

/* TEMPLATE TABS */
.tmpl-tabs{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px;}
.ttab{padding:4px 11px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;background:#fff;color:var(--ink-muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;font-family:inherit;}
.ttab:hover{border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal);}
.ttab.on{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-color:var(--ink);}
.tc{display:none;}.tc.on{display:block;}

/* BADGES */
.badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;}
.b-green{background:var(--green-light);color:#085041;}
.b-red{background:var(--red-light);color:#791F1F;}
.b-amber{background:var(--gold-light);color:#633806;}
.b-gray{background:#f0efe9;color:#5f5e5a;}
.b-blue{background:var(--blue-light);color:#0C447C;}

/* LETTER BLOCK */
.pb{background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.9;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:9px 0;}

/* COPY BUTTON */
.copy-btn{padding:5px 11px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:#fff;color:var(--ink-muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;font-family:inherit;}
.copy-btn:hover{background:var(--teal);color:#fff;border-color:var(--teal);}

/* NOTES */
.warn-note{background:var(--gold-light);border:1px solid #FAC775;border-radius:7px;padding:9px 13px;font-size:12px;color:#633806;margin-bottom:9px;}
.info-note{background:var(--blue-light);border:1px solid #B5D4F4;border-radius:7px;padding:9px 13px;font-size:12px;color:#0C447C;margin-bottom:9px;}
.checklist-row{display:flex;gap:7px;align-items:center;font-size:12px;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-soft);color:var(--ink-soft);}
.checklist-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}

/* FORM FIELDS */
.byo-field{margin-bottom:11px;}
.byo-field label{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-bottom:4px;letter-spacing:.3px;}
.byo-field input,.byo-field textarea,.byo-field select{width:100%;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;padding:8px 11px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;background:#fff;color:var(--ink);outline:none;transition:border .15s;}
.byo-field input:focus,.byo-field textarea:focus,.byo-field select:focus{border-color:var(--teal);}
.byo-field textarea{min-height:58px;resize:vertical;}

/* AI GENERATOR */
.gen-btn{background:var(--teal);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 22px;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
.gen-btn:hover{background:var(--aqua);}
.gen-btn:disabled{background:var(--border);color:var(--ink-muted);cursor:not-allowed;}
.output-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ink) 0%,#163a3f 100%);border-radius:12px;padding:20px 24px;margin-top:14px;display:none;border:1px solid var(--teal);}
.output-wrap.on{display:block;}
.out-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--aqua-light);margin-bottom:10px;}
.out-text{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);line-height:1.9;white-space:pre-wrap;}
.copy-out{margin-top:12px;background:transparent;color:var(--aqua-light);border:1px solid rgba(0,196,204,.35);border-radius:7px;padding:6px 14px;font-family:inherit;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.copy-out:hover{background:rgba(0,196,204,.12);}
.loading{display:none;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:11px 0;color:var(--ink-muted);font-size:12px;}
.loading.on{display:flex;}
.spin{width:15px;height:15px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-top-color:var(--teal);border-radius:50%;animation:sp .7s linear infinite;flex-shrink:0;}
@keyframes sp{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}

/* LANGUAGE BANK */
.lb-sec{margin-bottom:20px;}
.lb-sec h3{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:10px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;}
.pr{display:flex;gap:9px;margin-bottom:9px;}
.pc{flex:1;padding:11px 13px;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;}
.pc-ok{background:var(--green-light);border:1px solid #9FE1CB;color:#085041;}
.pc-no{background:var(--red-light);border:1px solid #F7C1C1;color:#791F1F;}
.pc-label{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:5px;}

/* RED FLAGS */
.fi{display:flex;gap:9px;align-items:flex-start;padding:9px 11px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:7px;}
.fi-red{background:var(--red-light);border:1px solid #F7C1C1;}
.fi-amber{background:var(--gold-light);border:1px solid #FAC775;}
.fi-red strong{color:#791F1F;font-size:12px;}.fi-red p{color:#a32d2d;font-size:12px;margin-top:2px;}
.fi-amber strong{color:#633806;font-size:12px;}.fi-amber p{color:#854f0b;font-size:12px;margin-top:2px;}

/* TRAINING */
.sc{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:10px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-card);}
.sc-q{background:var(--cream);border-radius:7px;padding:11px 13px;font-size:12px;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:11px;border-left:3px solid var(--ink-muted);line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);}
.sc-rev{display:none;margin-top:11px;}.sc-rev.on{display:block;}

/* QUICK REF */
.qr-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.qr-col{border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;border:1px solid;}
.qr-green{background:var(--green-light);border-color:#9FE1CB;}
.qr-red{background:var(--red-light);border-color:#F7C1C1;}
.qr-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.6px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:9px;}
.qr-green .qr-label{color:#085041;}.qr-red .qr-label{color:#791F1F;}
.qr-item{font-size:12px;padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid;line-height:1.5;}
.qr-green .qr-item{color:#085041;border-color:rgba(159,225,203,.5);}
.qr-red .qr-item{color:#791F1F;border-color:rgba(247,193,193,.5);}
.qr-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}

/* TABLE */
.ltat{width:100%;font-size:12px;border-collapse:collapse;}
.ltat th{text-align:left;padding:6px 9px;color:var(--ink-muted);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.4px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.ltat td{padding:7px 9px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-soft);vertical-align:top;}
.ltat tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}

/* ESCALATION */
.es{display:flex;gap:11px;padding:11px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.es:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.es-n{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--aqua-mid);border:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--teal);}
.es strong{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink);display:block;margin-bottom:2px;}
.es p{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);line-height:1.6;}

/* CARD WRAP */
.card-wrap{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:14px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-card);}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:768px){
  .header{padding:0 14px;height:56px;}
  .logo-mark{width:30px;height:30px;font-size:11px;border-radius:8px;}
  .logo-title{font-size:13px;}
  .logo-sub{display:none;}
  .tab-bar{padding:0 8px;top:56px;}
  .tab{padding:12px 10px;font-size:11px;}
  .main{padding:18px 14px 40px;}
  .hero{padding:22px 18px;}
  .hero h1{font-size:22px;}
  .pr{flex-direction:column;}
  .qr-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .stab{font-size:10px;padding:10px 10px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER — same as hub -->
<div class="header">
  <a class="logo" href="index.html">
    <div class="logo-mark">RW</div>
    <div><div class="logo-title">RWC Knowledge Hub</div><div class="logo-sub">Root Wellness Collective</div></div>
  </a>
</div>

<!-- TAB BAR — same as hub, Letters active -->
<div class="tab-bar">
  <a class="tab" href="index.html">🏠 Home</a>
  <a class="tab" href="index.html#browser" onclick="localStorage.setItem('rwc-tab','browser')">📋 SOP Browser</a>
  <a class="tab" href="index.html#chat" onclick="localStorage.setItem('rwc-tab','chat')">💬 SOP Assistant <span class="tab-ai">AI</span></a>
  <a class="tab active" href="letters.html">✉️ Letters</a>
</div>

<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<div class="main">

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Letter of Necessity System</div>
    <h1>Write <em>compliant</em> letters,<br>every time.</h1>
    <p>Decision tree · AI generator · 9 templates · Language bank · Red flags · Training · Escalation scripts</p>
  </div>

  <div class="hipaa">🔒 No client identifying info entered here — add name, DOB, phone in Practice Better after copying</div>

  <div class="subnav">
    <button class="stab on" onclick="showSub('tree',this)">🌳 Decision</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="showSub('gen',this)">✨ AI Draft</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="showSub('tpl',this)">📄 Templates</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="showSub('lang',this)">💬 Language</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="showSub('flags',this)">🚩 Red Flags</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="showSub('train',this)">🎓 Training</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="showSub('qref',this)">⚡ Quick Ref</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="showSub('esc',this)">📋 Escalation</button>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ DECISION TREE ═══ -->
  <div id="sub-tree" class="sub on">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;align-items:center;">
      <span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted);">Approval tiers:</span>
      <span class="tier t-self">Self-approve</span>
      <span class="tier t-mgmt">Flag Andrea</span>
      <span class="tier t-owner">Owner required</span>
    </div>
    <div class="dn dn-start" id="dn1"><div class="dn-title">1 — Do you have complete intake info?</div><p>All three required: (a) what the letter is for, (b) who receives it, (c) exactly what they require for acceptance.</p><button class="cbtn cbtn-stop" onclick="ds('dn-intake')">No — missing info</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn2')">Yes — all three confirmed</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-warn" id="dn-intake" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">Send intake request first</div><div class="pb" style="font-size:11.5px">Hi [Client first name],

To get your Letter of Necessity started, I need a few quick details:

1. What is the letter needed for?
2. Who will receive it?
3. What do they specifically require for it to be accepted?
4. Is there a deadline?</div><button class="cbtn" onclick="dtReset()">↩ Start over once intake is complete</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-q" id="dn2" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">2 — Does the recipient require any of the following?</div><p>A diagnosis · Named medical condition · ICD/CPT codes · Physician certification · FMLA form · Disability determination · Government statement on medical status · ADA formal certification</p><button class="cbtn cbtn-stop" onclick="ds('dn-strict')">Yes — any of the above</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn3')">No — none of the above</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-q" id="dn-strict" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">2b — What kind of strict-standard request?</div><button class="cbtn cbtn-stop" onclick="ds('dn-hardstop')">Requires diagnosis, codes, or licensed provider cert</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-blue" onclick="ds('dn-govt')">Government / agency — statement on medical status</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-blue" onclick="ds('dn-licensed')">Letter under practitioner's actual licensure</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-stop" id="dn-hardstop" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">Stop — cannot provide this letter</div><p>Decline and close. Do not offer workarounds.</p><div class="pb" style="font-size:11.5px">Hi [Client first name],

Thank you for reaching out. After reviewing your request, we aren't able to provide this letter — it requires documentation (diagnosis, codes, or licensed provider certification) outside our scope as health coaches.

We'd recommend connecting with your primary care physician for this type of documentation.</div><button class="cbtn" onclick="dtReset()">↩ Start over</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-blue" id="dn-govt" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">Government / agency — narrow statement only</div><p>Nothing about conditions or work capacity. Flag for Andrea before sending.</p><button class="cbtn cbtn-blue" onclick="goTmpl('govt')">Open government statement template →</button><span class="tier t-mgmt" style="display:inline-flex;margin-top:8px;">Flag Andrea before sending</span><button class="cbtn" style="margin-top:8px;" onclick="dtReset()">↩ Start over</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-blue" id="dn-licensed" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">Licensed practitioner track — different rules</div><p>Clinical language, diagnoses, credentials in signature permitted. Practitioner reviews and signs. Owner must be aware.</p><button class="cbtn cbtn-blue" onclick="goTmpl('licensed')">Open licensed practitioner template →</button><span class="tier t-owner" style="display:inline-flex;margin-top:8px;">Owner must be aware</span><button class="cbtn" style="margin-top:8px;" onclick="dtReset()">↩ Start over</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-q" id="dn3" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">3 — Does the letter need clinical reasoning?</div><p>Does it need to explain <em>why</em> something is beneficial beyond general health coach opinion?</p><button class="cbtn" onclick="ds('dn-pract')">Yes — needs clinical context from practitioner</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn4')">No — general health coach opinion is enough</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-warn" id="dn-pract" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">Get practitioner input first — then translate</div><p>Ask the practitioner why this recommendation benefits this client. Convert their answer to compliant health coach language. See Language tab → "Translating practitioner input."</p><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn4')">Input received — continue to letter type</button></div>
    <div class="dn dn-q" id="dn4" style="display:none"><div class="dn-title">4 — What type of letter?</div><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn-landlord')">Landlord accommodation</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn-fsa')">FSA / HSA / Christian healthshare reimbursement</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn-therapy')">Therapy modality (red light, PEMF, hyperbaric, sauna)</button><button class="cbtn cbtn-go" onclick="ds('dn-supp')">Supplement or wellness product necessity</button><button class="cbtn" onclick="ds('dn-other')">Other accommodation (school, workplace, travel, grant)</button></div>
